<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Establishing the BNB Security Framework</h3>



<p>To establish the BNB Security Framework, undergo a rigorous process of Binance Coin security audits. </p>



<p>These audits ensure that Binance Coin (BNB) possesses robust security features and adheres to the highest standards of safety. The security framework encompasses various aspects, including encryption methods, wallet security, fraud prevention, network security protocols, transaction verification, regulatory compliance, smart contract safety, and security audits.</p>



<p>To provide a comprehensive understanding of the BNB Security Framework, the following table highlights key elements and their significance:</p>



