<li><strong>Robust testing:</strong> Thoroughly test the smart contracts using various scenarios and edge cases to ensure their reliability and security. This includes conducting unit tests, integration tests, and stress tests to identify and rectify any potential issues before they can be exploited.</li>
</ul>



