<li><strong>Double-check transaction details: </strong>Before confirming any transaction, carefully review the recipient&#8217;s address and the amount you&#8217;re sending. Any errors can result in irreversible losses.</li>



<li><strong>Verify transaction on the blockchain: </strong>Once the transaction is sent, you can use a block explorer or Binance&#8217;s transaction history to confirm its status and ensure it has been successfully processed.</li>



