<li><strong>Mitigates Risk of Password Theft</strong>: Even if your password is compromised, an attacker would still need the second factor, which significantly reduces the chances of unauthorized access and fraudulent activities.</li>



<li><strong>Compliance with Regulatory Standards</strong>: Enabling 2FA aligns with the regulatory compliance requirements set by crypto exchanges like Binance, ensuring a safer environment for trading and storage of Binance Coin.</li>
